channel.title: Oh for god sakes, someone must know this!
channel.description:
I hav all the int's for making new items, objects, npcs, ect... but I DONT KNOW HOW TO UNPACK/REPACK CACHE!!! I spent 3 months looking for the chance to learn how to make new items, and the only thing that is stopping me is not being able to find a program that unpacks cache, and no nowing HOW to unpack cache. Plus I hear repacking is ALOT harder. Can someone PLZ help me!!!!!!!!! And I REALLY hate begging, but I just cant find the stupid link. And all the links that I do find are broken. I can never trust mopar to hold an old file, because its deleted like a few days after its posted, or wrongly locked... PLZ HELP!!!! lol, srry for begging, and I dont mean to be mean to any mods/admins.
If you have to, pm me!!!
Also, My email is helboundz@yahoo.com PLZ HELP!!![br][size=1]Posted on: September 10, 2007, 03:32:19 PM[/size][hr]Oh for god sakes. I just found out how to unpack, but how do you repack??? For god sakes, someone must know!!
